Interface AisMessage

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    AisPosition, AisShipStatic
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AisAidToNavigation, AisBaseStation, AisMessageOther, AisPositionA, AisPositionB, AisPositionBExtended, AisShipStaticA

    public interface AisMessage
    An AIS Message according to ITU R M 1371-4 ( a copy is in cts-adapter-ais/docs).
    Author:
    dxm

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      int getMessageId()
      Returns the ais message id.

    • Method Detail

      • getMessageId

        int getMessageId()
        Returns the ais message id. For example Class A Position reports are either 1, 2, or 3.
        Returns:

      • getSource

        String getSource()
        Returns the source of the ais message. The source is not available in the ais message itself but may be provided in the tag block of the NMEA message that contains the ais message.
        Returns:
